title: Index of Machine Tool Shipments, Value (Monthly Average of Shipments) for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1925-1934 (2)--Original Data, 1925-1934 Data Covers The Dollar Value Of Shipments. Figures Are Based On The Returns Of 50-60 Firms, Representing One-Third Of The Industry. Source: Survey Of Current Business And Its Supplements.

This NBER data series m01169a appears on the NBER website in Chapter 1 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter01.html.
